00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:31,300
Hello.

284
00:19:32,930 --> 00:19:35,090
Okay, I'll be right back.

285
00:19:37,220 --> 00:19:39,200
I'll go first.

286
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:41,590
